Global Electric Rotary Shavers Market Insights
Electric Rotary Shavers Market size was valued at USD 3.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Electric Rotary Shavers Market Overview
The electric rotary shavers market has experienced significant growth over recent years, with an estimated market value of approximately USD 3.2 billion in 2024. This growth is driven by factors such as increasing demand for convenient grooming solutions, innovations in shaving technology, and a growing focus on male grooming products. The market is expected to continue its upward trajectory, with a forecasted compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6% through 2030. Rising disposable incomes and the growing trend of personal care and hygiene are key contributors to the market's expansion.

